  <hidden>true</hidden>
  <content>This is a legacy, unprefixed Confluence bridge for the Userlister macro. Please use UserList macro instead.

== Parameters ==

|= Parameter |= Name |= Description |= Default
| groups | Groups | List of Confluence user groups, separated by a comma. A wildcard means all wiki users. |
| online | Online | Ignored parameter, present for compatibility purpose only |

== Examples ==

=== All users ===

{{code}}
{{userlister groups="*"/}}
{{/code}}

{{userlister groups="*"/}}

=== All administrators ===

{{code}}
{{userlister groups="administrators"/}}
{{/code}}

{{userlister groups="administrators"/}}</content>
